{"sha": "4c851792ac28c6fb09828a036b7fe3d4e1707033", "node_id": "MDY6Q29tbWl0NzI0NzEyOjRjODUxNzkyYWMyOGM2ZmIwOTgyOGEwMzZiN2ZlM2Q0ZTE3MDcwMzM=", "commit": {"author": {"name": "Shen-Ta Hsieh", "email": "beststeve@secondstate.io", "date": "2020-07-31T08:52:59Z"}, "committer": {"name": "Shen-Ta Hsieh", "email": "beststeve@secondstate.io", "date": "2020-07-31T09:01:16Z"}, "message": "Fix std::fs::File::metadata permission on WASI target\n\nPreviously `std::fs::File::metadata` on wasm32-wasi would call `fd_filestat_get`\nto get metadata associated with fd, but that fd is opened without\nRIGHTS_FD_FILESTAT_GET right, so it will failed on correctly implemented WASI\nenvironment.\n\nThis change instead to add the missing rights when opening an fd.", "tree": {"sha": "6e88d9e80f9ceecc8e3c4bdeac5e92bbf2cddf15", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/git/trees/6e88d9e80f9ceecc8e3c4bdeac5e92bbf2cddf15"}, "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/git/commits/4c851792ac28c6fb09828a036b7fe3d4e1707033", "comment_count": 0, "verification": {"verified": true, "reason": "valid", "signature": "-----BEGIN PGP SIGNATURE-----\n\niHUEABYIAB0WIQQZKo+/j/9wM9PGLXXff+0rBJL6dwUCXyPd8gAKCRDff+0rBJL6\ndwomAP4/LlGPfnm8jlaMkBT2NVcJVJ6jxykzKJlep0tJBTXXPQD8DBPI19GShTFq\nu+XZz47g0czbi+HX6KbVQPgCi+wl0AM=\n=6bIb\n-----END PGP SIGNATURE-----", "payload": "tree 6e88d9e80f9ceecc8e3c4bdeac5e92bbf2cddf15\nparent ac91673d895a0c578ed773e1280bdde8adb87b8c\nauthor Shen-Ta Hsieh <beststeve@secondstate.io> 1596185579 +0000\ncommitter Shen-Ta Hsieh <beststeve@secondstate.io> 1596186076 +0000\n\nFix std::fs::File::metadata permission on WASI target\n\nPreviously `std::fs::File::metadata` on wasm32-wasi would call `fd_filestat_get`\nto get metadata associated with fd, but that fd is opened without\nRIGHTS_FD_FILESTAT_GET right, so it will failed on correctly implemented WASI\nenvironment.\n\nThis change instead to add the missing rights when opening an fd.\n"}}, "url": "https://api.github.com/repo